result.reason: Printer redirection is implemented via RdpProtocol.cs (AdvancedSettings2.RedirectPrinters) but the issue lacks details on what 'not working correctly' means — whether the checkbox is ignored, printers don't appear, or only specific printer types fail.
result.approach: Request reproduction steps: which RDP version, which printer type (network vs local), whether RedirectPrinters checkbox is saved/loaded correctly, and whether the issue is at the RDP ActiveX level or mRemoteNG UI level
